{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2019/02/25/javascript 获取 unsigned int.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"261cc629-90f3-5e5a-8663-33452dc3d177","excerpt":"JavaScript 获取 Unsigned Int JavaScript 默认是64位有符号的整型，可以利用移位符号解决，但不是>>2而是>>>0 最好不要使用 >> ，推荐使用 >>> 因为最左边一位会被解析成符号位，当数字溢出时，会被解析成负数。 当然按照这种方式eslint…","html":"<h1>JavaScript 获取 Unsigned Int</h1>\n<p>JavaScript 默认是64位有符号的整型，可以利用移位符号解决，但不是>>2而是>>>0</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">4136517969</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* b == -39612332 */</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">4136517969</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">>>></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* b == 4136517969 */</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>最好不要使用 >> ，推荐使用 >>> 因为最左边一位会被解析成符号位，当数字溢出时，会被解析成负数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>当然按照这种方式eslint的默认配置是不允许的，所以可以借助 Unit32Array.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">4136517969</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* b == 4136517969 */</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2019/02/25/javascript 获取 unsigned int.html","date":"February 25, 2019","title":"javascript 获取 unsigned int"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2019/02/25/javascript 获取 unsigned int.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2019/02/24/种草清单.html","title":"种草清单"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2019/03/08/读《元朝那些事儿》.html","title":"读《元朝那些事儿》"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}}}}}